      <section class="mb-4">
        <p>
          This Cookie Policy explains how VENICARA (“we”, “us”, or “our”) uses cookies and similar technologies to enhance your experience on our website (the “Site”).  
          By accessing or using our Site, you consent to the use of cookies as described in this Cookie Policy. If you do not agree, you can adjust your browser settings to disable cookies, though this may affect your experience on the Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Changes Section -->
      <section class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-semibold">Changes to This Cookie Policy</h4>
        <p>
          We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices, technology, or legal requirements. When we make changes, we will post the revised policy on the Site and update the “Last Updated” date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- What Are Cookies Section -->
      <section class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-semibold">What Are Cookies?</h4>
        <p>
          Cookies are small text files stored on your device (computer, tablet, or mobile) when you visit a website. They help us recognize your device, remember your preferences, and improve your shopping experience. We also use similar technologies like web beacons, pixels, or tags to collect information about your interactions with our Site.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Types of Cookies Section -->
      <section class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-semibold">Types of Cookies We Use</h4>
        <p>We use the following types of cookies on our Site to provide a seamless experience:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Essential Cookies:</strong> These cookies are necessary for the Site to function properly, such as enabling you to log in, add perfumes to your cart, and complete purchases.</li>
          <li><strong>Performance Cookies:</strong> These collect anonymous data about how you use the Site (e.g., pages visited, time spent) to help us improve its functionality.</li>
          <li><strong>Functional Cookies:</strong> These remember your preferences (e.g., language, currency, or saved items) to personalize your experience.</li>
          <li><strong>Advertising Cookies:</strong> These track your browsing habits to show you relevant ads for VENICARA perfumes on our Site or third-party platforms.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- How We Use Cookies Section -->
      <section class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-semibold">How We Use Cookies</h4>
        <p>
          Cookies help us provide, protect, and improve our services. Specifically, we use cookies to:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Authenticate your account and keep you logged in.</li>
          <li>Track your shopping activity (e.g., items viewed, added to cart, or purchased) to enhance your experience.</li>
          <li>Analyze Site performance and user behavior to optimize our platform.</li>
          <li>Deliver personalized advertisements for our perfumes based on your interests.</li>
          <li>Prevent fraudulent activity and ensure the security of your transactions.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <!-- Managing Cookies Section -->
      <section class="mb-4">
        <h4 class="fw-semibold">Managing Your Cookie Preferences</h4>
        <p>
          You can control how cookies are used on our Site:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Cookie Consent:</strong> Upon visiting our Site, you may see a cookie consent banner allowing you to accept or customize cookie settings.</li>
          <li><strong>Browser Settings:</strong> Most browsers allow you to block or delete cookies. However, disabling essential cookies may limit Site functionality, such as preventing you from placing orders.</li>
          <li><strong>Opt-Out of Advertising:</strong> You can opt out of targeted advertising cookies through third-party services like the Digital Advertising Alliance or Network Advertising Initiative.</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          To manage your preferences, visit our cookie settings page or contact our support team for assistance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <!-- Closing -->
      <section>
